.br
.ps +1
\fBNote\fR
.ps -1
.br
.sp
This man page only documents the hardware\-specific features of the \fBvictronups\fR driver\&. For information about the core driver, see \fBnutupsdrv\fR(8)\&.
.sp .5v
.RE
.SH "SUPPORTED HARDWARE"
.sp
The victronups driver should recognize all Victron models that use a serial protocol at 1200 bps\&. These include Match Lite, Match and the NetUps line\&.
.sp
The Match Lite line may only report a handful of variables\&. This is usually not a bug \(em they just don\(cqt support anything else\&.
