.SH "EXTRA ARGUMENTS"
.sp
This driver supports the following optional setting in the \fBups.conf\fR(5):
.PP
\fBmodelname\fR=\fIname\fR
.RS 4
Set model name
.RE
.PP
\fBusd\fR=\fIdelay\fR
.RS 4
